      <div class="row"><span class="lbl">Key Principle</span><span class="val">Ulcers develop due to an imbalance between mucosal <span class="hl">defensive factors</span> (mucus, bicarbonate, prostaglandins, mucosal blood flow) and <span class="hl">aggressive factors</span> (gastric acid, pepsin, NSAIDs, <i>H. pylori</i>)</span></div>
